，還在習近平面前說最古老的文化是埃及文化。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，昨天川普在習近平帶領下參觀了紫禁城，沒想到川普當場變成歷史老師，大秀自己對中國歷史的了解，直說「中國的歷史可以追溯到5千年前，或者更早」。<br />\n<br />\n聽到川普這番話，<span style=\"color: red;\">習近平補充說，「有文字的是3千年。」沒想到<span style=\"font-size: large;\">川普又補了一句，「我想最古老的文化是埃及文化，有8千年歷史。」</span>習近平<strong>愣了一下</strong>，隨後認同這說法，不過他對川普強調，「文化沒有斷過流的，始終傳承下來的只有中國。」</span><br />\n<br />\n習近平還進一步解釋，「我們這些人黑頭髮、黃皮膚傳承下來，我們叫龍的傳人。」川普聽完這段話則是大笑三聲表示認同。<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2247989\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2247989&d=jSwC3uiGN3vC7JBO22xqb%2FM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=85467cf5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2247989&h=3417c367\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2247989</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n第一次食蛋榚<br />\n第二次講古老文化<br />\n兩次侵侵都可以令習呆呆愣了一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c69a6f20687d76df0feea5a6f2736cd57adefe0","tid":462908,"uid":810,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T05:16:02.000Z","msg":"川普聽完這段話則是大笑三聲表示認同。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5cf26f69ad36453ffb750787c5ea24befd837dc","tid":462908,"uid":83328,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T05:20:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>特朗普句句有骨, 習總唔好忍佢開佢波啦, 駛怕佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/VXpQwC4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FVXpQwC4.gif&h=19c1dae1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e513605a8c1e8ba421babcb08914518e09de45e","tid":462908,"uid":73262,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201